net.sf.ehcache.pool
Interface PoolableStore

All Superinterfaces:
Store
All Known Implementing Classes:
DiskStore, MemoryStore, NotifyingMemoryStore
public interface PoolableStore
extends Store

A poolable store reports its resource usage to a Pool.

Author:
Ludovic Orban
